    "discogs_id": 14527117,
    "name": "Astral Fortress",
    "profile": "Astral Fortress is a project created in January 2023 by Talamandas (Holy Martyr) and Enharioth (Shardana/The Blacktones).\r\n\r\nThe style of the music is a unique blend of old school Melodic Death and Black Metal, combined with experimental and avant-garde passages.\r\nThis peculiar approach makes the music still rooted in the scene of the 90’s, with powerful and melodic bands like Unanimated and Dissection, the minimalism of early Darkthrone and the straightforward assault of Morbid Angel as well.\r\n\r\nEven the nickname was taken from the glorious past, inspired by the song “Enslaved from the Astral Fortress”, contained on the seminal album Vittra by Naglfar.\r\nThe lyrics are based on the world of Lovecraft, space, astrophysics and horror movies/books (the Lighthouse, Rosemary’s Baby), making the album grim, dark but at the same time cold and melodic.\r\n\r\nAstral Fortress are:\r\n\r\nEnharioth (Vocals)\r\nTalamandas (Guitars)\r\nTat0 (Bass)\r\nMaze of Torment (Drums)\r\n",
